00:52:13,200 --> 00:52:16,480
you need to change
the whole 1.2.

675
00:52:16,560 --> 00:52:18,720
Say that again.

676
00:52:18,760 --> 00:52:22,960
To get the five for six,
you need to change the whole 1.2.
That's the deal you made.

677
00:52:25,440 --> 00:52:28,200
That's exactly not
the deal I made.

678
00:52:28,280 --> 00:52:31,280
- That's the deal...
